rob tyler is a film and digital video artist from portland , oregon , usa who has created long form works of ambient video art . from 1998 to 2005 , tyler 's color & modulation was created by hand-painting roughly 15,000 frames of 16 mm film with acrylic paints , magic markers and fingernail polish . in 2006 , rob tyler was named finalist in colorcalm 's international design competition curated by graphic designer peter saville .